    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;さんって、
弓を使った攻撃がお上手なんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm impressed Mister &lt;Chester&gt;! Your skill with the bow is excellent!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、まぁな。
それから、オレのことは&lt;Chester&gt;でいいぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, thanks. About that, please just call me "&lt;Chester&gt;."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、わ、わかりました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>U-understood!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44416</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それからその敬語じゃなくて、
フツーで頼む</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Again, don't be so polite all the time. Lighten up a bit.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44524</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、は、はい、わかりまし……
わかる……わかったわ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-yes, undertoo—G-Got it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……何やってんだ、&lt;Mel&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatcha doing, &lt;Mel&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こ、こんな感じで
い、いいのかな……&lt;Chester&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is t-this okay, &lt;Chester&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふふん、いい感じだ。
そんな感じでお願いするよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hahaha. Yes it's great. Please speak like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わ、わかりました、&lt;Chester&gt;さん……
あっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Understood, Mister &lt;Chester&gt;—Oh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_042_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま……無理することはないさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, well. There's no use to it, is there?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
